---

<section
  class="relative pt-24 md:pt-32 lg:pt-[180px] pb-16 md:pb-24 flex flex-col justify-start items-center px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-0 w-full overflow-hidden font-sans"
  aria-labelledby="hero-heading"
>
  <div class="absolute top-[10%] left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-20 md:opacity-30">
    <img
      src="/mask-group-pattern.svg"
      alt=""
      loading="eager"
      decoding="async"
      class="w-[800px] md:w-[1400px] lg:w-[2000px] h-auto mix-blend-multiply"
    />
  </div>

  
  
  <div class="w-full max-w-[900px] flex flex-col justify-center items-center relative z-20">
    
    
    <h1
      id="hero-heading"
      class="w-full text-center flex flex-col text-[#1A2F1D] text-[2.5rem] leading-[1.1] sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-[72px] font-semibold tracking-tight lg:leading-[1.05]"
    >
      Gymple. El software
      <span class="text-[#38523C]">que automatiza tu gimnasio.</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="w-full max-w-[640px] mt-4 md:mt-6 text-center text-[#38523C] text-base md:text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-[1.5] font-normal tracking-normal px-4">
      Sistema de gestión para centros de entrenamientos  con cobranza automática por WhatsApp, control de socios, membresías y finanzas.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4 relative z-10 mt-10 md:mt-12">
    <a
      href="#contacto"
      class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-3.5 bg-[#1A2F1D] text-white rounded-full text-base md:text-[17px] font-medium hover:bg-[#000000] hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] transition-all duration-300 flex justify-center items-center"
    >
      Probar gratis 14 días
    </a>
    <a
      href="mailto:hola@gymple.com"
      class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-3.5 bg-[#f5f5f7] text-[#1A2F1D] rounded-full text-base md:text-[17px] font-medium hover:bg-[#e8e8ed] active:bg-[#d1d1d6] transition-colors flex justify-center items-center"
    >
      Agendar demo
    </a>
  </div>
</section>